.DT
query_visible
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_visible

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_visible -  This method returns the current visibility status of this creator in respect to the other object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_visible(object thing)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the object to test the visibility against
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 if not invisible, non-zero if invisible

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/creator/wiz_file_comm.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the current visibility status of this creator
in respect to the other object.  This does the allow level checking
and all sorts of exciting things.


It will return 1 for creator invisible, 2 for lord invisible, 3 for high lord invisible.
.EP

